OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783982881
OL,3,CMastermind behind E88m Louvre heist
OL,4,Cthought they 'could have stolen more'
OL,6,FPolice also have two other men in
OL,7,Fdetention, identified as Slimane K.
OL,8,Fand Rachid H. and claim they were the
OL,9,Fother half of the four-man team who
OL,10,Fcarried out the operation.
OL,12,FLe Monde reported Abdoulaye N had told
OL,13,Fmagistrates these two men were not the
OL,14,Fcorrect people and that the real
OL,15,Fmastermind of the operation was
OL,16,Finvolved in the heist.
OL,18,FInvestigators are still not sure of
OL,19,Fthe full story and are considering the
OL,20,Fpossibility that there was no real
OL,21,Fmastermind involved in the plot.
OL,26,@kD@SOk
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
