OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783982881
OL,3,CMastermind behind E88m Louvre heist
OL,4,Cthought they 'could have stolen more'
OL,6,FThe heist stunned France and led to
OL,7,Fthe resignation of the Louvre's
OL,8,Fdirector, Laurence des Cars.
OL,10,FSince the theft, security at the
OL,11,FLouvre has been transformed after its
OL,12,Foperators admitted it had been lacking.
OL,14,FSeveral of its most valuable items
OL,15,Fhave also been transferred to the Bank
OL,16,Fof France.
OL,18,FThe Louvre has also hiked prices for
OL,19,Fvisitors from non-EU countries in
OL,20,Frecent months, with it rising from 22
OL,21,Feuros (#19.25) to 32 euros (#28).
OL,26,@kD@SOk
